'''[[empty]] [[product]]''' (''plural'' '''empty products''')

#{{arithmetic}} The result of [[multiply]]ing no numbers (defined in order to be able to extend certain mathematical concepts, such as the product of ''n'' numbers, to the case where ''n'' = 0).

